						"description": "List system params with pagination and optional filters.\n\nQuery Parameters:\n- page: Page number (default: 1)\n- page_size: Items per page (default: 10, max: 100)\n- order_field: Field to order by (id|name|preset_id|is_active|created_at|updated_at)\n- order_type: Order direction (asc|desc)\n- name: Filter by name (LIKE search)\n- is_active: Filter by active status (true|false)\n- preset_id: Filter by preset ID\n- preset_name: Filter by preset name (LIKE search)\n\nResponse includes pagination metadata."
