									"description": "System params ID to update"
								}
							]
						},
						"description": "Update an existing system params record. All fields are optional (partial update).\n\nPath Parameters:\n- id: System params ID (required)\n\nRequest Body (all fields optional):\n- is_active: Active status (boolean)\n- preset_name: Preset name (string)\n- params_config: Parameter configuration as JSON object (jsonb)\n\nNote: name and preset_id cannot be updated after creation. They are immutable fields.\n\nOnly provided fields will be updated. Returns the updated system params record."
					},
